        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Virgilianus qui bixit <note>sic</note> annus <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/>XXX et <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elia</ex></expan> Ursilla oxor <note>sic</note> eius qui <lb n="3"/>se vivi sibi urdenaverunt <note>sic</note> <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>unc</abbr></expan> sar&amp;lt;c=T&amp;gt;ofa<lb break="no" n="4"/>gum si quis autem voluerit super h<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>ec</abbr></expan> d</ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>uo corpora punere <note>sic</note> infere&amp;lt;t=H&amp;gt; <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">san</supplied>c</abbr><ex>tae</ex></expan> ec<expan><ex>c</ex><abbr>lisiae</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> argenti libras quinque<surplus>m</surplus> 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Am rechten Akroter des Sarkophagdeckels in einen Kreis eingeschriebenes Christusmonogramm mit darin eingeschriebenem A und ω. Fortsetzung des Textes (ab Z. 5) auch dem Giebeldreieck des Deckels.</p>
            </div>
